# Kanban Board Project Rules

This is a standalone kanban board application repository.

## Project Structure

- `src/` - React application source code
- `docs/` - Project-specific documentation, tickets, and audit logs
- `scripts/` - Utility scripts (e.g., sync-tickets.js)

## Development

- Run `npm run dev` to start the development server
- Run `npm run build` to build for production
- Run `npm run sync-tickets` to sync tickets between docs and Supabase

